    "description": {
      "value": "<p>Techniques: Purple </p><p></p><p>When your Puppet Tool would not move on your turn, a blue sigil of chakra appears on the ground within a 10-foot radius of it.</p><p> All allied creatures, excluding you and your Puppet Tool, gain a +1 to AC and Strength, Dexterity, and Constitution saving throws, for the first attack made against them and saving throw they make per round respectively.</p><p> At Higher Levels: You may take this upgrade as a Silver tier upgrade to also gain its effects when It activates.</p><p> Furthermore, you can take it as a Gold upgrade, to increase the bonuses to a +2.</p><p></p>",
